metadata.name: nostalgic landscape 55
metadata.description:
nostalgic landscape 55 (roll 02), 2022
7680 x 6144 pixels, 72 dpi
unique edition

/

nostalgic landscapes are images of places i'm no longer sure i visited. when i doubt my memory, i make sure to check that i have an image to prove i went there, but i don't remember how i got there or how it all happened. fortunately, the memories are good.

nostalgic landscapes is a series of images produced as rephotographs. each collection/series consists of thirty-six images, as on a roll of film.
